-- Lehman moving to sell all of investment management unit: report
-- 
-- Mon Sep 15, 2008 2:16pm EDT
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2008/09/15/us-lehman-investmentfirm-idUSHER56326120080915

 

 (Reuters) - Lehman Brothers Holdings Incis moving to sell 100 percent of its investment management unit, Wall Street Journal reported on Monday. 

 * May sell investment management unit as soon as this week-Wall Street Journal * Potential list of buyers for investment management unit narrowed to Bain Capital, Hellman & Friedman and Clayton Dubilier & Rice-Wall Street Journal